   <description>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">The audit of ARA Centro and PP2 was undertaken in&#xA0;May 2017, auditors&apos; visit to ARA centro took place 14 - 20 May 2017. The audit&#xA0;concerned the period 1 January, 2016-30 April, 2017 . The audit report was submitted to Sida on 30 June 2017 and was unqualified.
However, Sida&apos;s own&#xA0;records showed that there was a difference between the amount reported by the project and the full amount paid out by Sida. Dialogue with KPMG and the project partners continued throughout the fall 2017. It has now been confirmed that the errors in reporting have taken place in periods prior to the one audited by KPMG. The report has therefore been approved and the invoices for audit paid.</narrative>
   </description>
